Edit profile interactively

Usage: wheelctl profile edit [OPTIONS] <PROFILE>

Arguments:
  <PROFILE>  Profile path or ID

Options:
      --field <FIELD>  Field to edit (e.g., base.ffbGain)
      --json           Output in JSON format for machine parsing
  -v, --verbose...     Verbose logging
      --value <VALUE>  New value
  -h, --help           Print help
